  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 ASME V&V 40 credibility factors assessed; all actively assessed factors achieve or exceed their required credibility levels. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification performed across 5 flow-speed combinations. Decision: Accepted.",
